OL,3,CDrug driving 'shockingly prevalent'
OL,4,Cand 'exceeding' drink drive arrests
OL,6,FAccording to government figures, the
OL,7,Fpercentage of road fatalities where
OL,8,Fdrugs have been found in a deceased
OL,9,Fdrivers' system has nearly doubled
OL,10,Fsince the law was introduced, from 11%
OL,11,Fto 19%.
OL,13,FMany road safety campaigners fear the
OL,14,Ftrue extent of drug driving is going
OL,15,Funderreported due to testing
OL,16,Frequirements, which can delay or even
OL,17,Fdeny prosecution.
OL,19,FNick Smith accompanied a Thames Valley
OL,20,FRoads Policing unit on the hunt for
OL,21,Fdrug drivers
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
