OL,3,CDrug driving 'shockingly prevalent'
OL,4,Cand 'exceeding' drink drive arrests
OL,6,FThames Valley Police (TVP) arrested
OL,7,F432 people for both drink and drug
OL,8,Foffences over their December crackdown
OL,9,Fcampaign. Of those detained, 196
OL,10,Fpeople were arrested for alcohol,
OL,11,Fwhile it was 236 for other drugs.
OL,13,FOfficers say it is now not uncommon on
OL,14,Fany given day to see more drug drivers
OL,15,Ftaken to custody than drivers testing
OL,16,Fabove the legal limit for alcohol.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
