OL,3,CDrug driving 'shockingly prevalent'
OL,4,Cand 'exceeding' drink drive arrests
OL,6,FLiam Calvert, a traffic Officer from
OL,7,FThames Valley Police, said: "The rise
OL,8,Fis just incredible. You could go out
OL,9,Fevery single day and arrest drug
OL,10,Fdrivers, whether it's delivery
OL,11,Fdrivers, taxi drivers, lorry
OL,12,Fdrivers... it's those kind of people
OL,13,Fthat surprise me.
OL,15,F"They're driving on the motorway,
OL,16,Fdriving a 44-ton lorry, taking
OL,17,Ffamilies to the airport, and these
OL,18,Fdrivers are under the influence."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
