OL,6,FThe process of proving someone is
OL,7,Fabove a specified limit for drug
OL,8,Fdriving is a lot more resource-
OL,9,Fintensive than for drink driving.
OL,11,FMany road traffic officers carry drug
OL,12,Fwipes, which take a saliva sample and
OL,13,Fact like a lateral flow test. They
OL,14,Fwill indicate a positive detection of
OL,15,Fcocaine or cannabis within a few
OL,16,Fminutes by the roadside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
