OL,4,Cand 'exceeding' drink drive arrests
OL,6,FThe driver is usually permitted to
OL,7,Fcontinue to be on the road until the
OL,8,Flab results come through, a
OL,9,Fprosecution can be made, and then a
OL,10,Fban or suspension will only be
OL,11,Fimplemented upon conviction.
OL,13,FCompare that with an evidential breath
OL,14,Ftest for alcohol, which can provide
OL,15,Fresults within minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
