OL,6,FFurthermore, police drugs wipes under
OL,7,Fcurrent guidelines can only test for
OL,8,Fcocaine or cannabis. This means that
OL,9,Fan initial indication that a driver
OL,10,Fmay have taken a different substance
OL,11,Fis harder to spot and can be missed.
OL,13,FEan Lewin, the owner of D.Tec, a
OL,14,Fcompany which supplies drugs wipes to
OL,15,Fpolice forces and also saliva testing
OL,16,Fkits to the commercial sector, said:
OL,17,F"There is a growing risk from drug
OL,18,Fdrivers and specialist roads policing
OL,19,Fofficers need a more efficient,
OL,20,Fquicker prosecution system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
