OL,6,F"I know of one case where an offender
OL,7,Fwas stopped and checked eight times
OL,8,Fbefore the blood from the first
OL,9,Foffence came back, and they were able
OL,10,Fto take him to court.
OL,12,F"Accredited laboratories can take
OL,13,Fmany, many months before the results
OL,14,Fcome back, at which time, shockingly,
OL,15,Fthe driver is still allowed to be on
OL,16,Fthe road."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
