OL,6,FSome other countries like France and
OL,7,FAustralia take a larger saliva sample
OL,8,Fat the roadside, which is then
OL,9,Fanalysed and can return results within
OL,10,Fdays. In Australia's case, in some
OL,11,Fstates, they can suspend the driver's
OL,12,Flicence while they await trial.
OL,14,FLinzi Stewart's brother Tim was killed
OL,15,Fwhen he was hit by a driver who'd
OL,16,Ftaken cocaine. The same driver was
OL,17,Factually waiting on test results from
OL,18,Fa previous drug stop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
