OL,6,FShe said: "He was convicted of drug
OL,7,Fdriving in 2021, and he'd also
OL,8,Fpreviously hit a car 10 days before
OL,9,Fhitting Tim. He was intoxicated then,
OL,10,Fas well.
OL,12,F"If he'd had some bail conditions put
OL,13,Fon him or his license revoked, Tim
OL,14,Fwould possibly still be alive. We do
OL,15,Fhave issues with the law the way it is
OL,16,Fnow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
