OL,6,F"Too many innocent people are being
OL,7,Fkilled. I know of one case where an
OL,8,Foffender was stopped and checked eight
OL,9,Ftimes before the blood from the first
OL,10,Foffence came back, and they were able
OL,11,Fto take him to court."
OL,13,FLinzi is now appealing for law changes
OL,14,Fto introduce license suspensions as
OL,15,Fpart of bail conditions for drivers
OL,16,Fwho are suspected of committing drink
OL,17,For drug driving offences. Her petition
OL,18,Fhas gathered more than 150,000
OL,19,Fsignatures.
